msgid "Make sure you clean your house and yard regularly. Childrenâ€™s poo should be thrown in the toilet, and animal poo and ğŸ“„rubbish should be removed."
msgstr "Qiniseka ukuthi uhlanza indlu yakho negceke njalo. Indle yezingane kufanele ilahlwe endlini yangasese, futhi indle yezilwane kanye ğŸ“„nodoti kufanele kukhishwe."

#. type=text
