#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "â–¶ï¸ Press play to learn the five 5ï¸âƒ£ tips to keep your food and water safe âœ… "
msgstr "â–¶ï¸ Cindezela okuthi dlala ukuze ufunde ngamacebiso amahlanu 5ï¸âƒ£ okugcina ukudla kwakho namanzi kuphephile âœ… "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Here are 5ï¸âƒ£ tips to keep your food and water safe. "
