#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1ï¸âƒ£ **Access Safe Water, When You Can. Treat It When You Canâ€™t**"
msgstr "1ï¸âƒ£ **Sebenzisa Amanzi Aphephile, Uma Ungakwazi. Uwahlanze Lapho Ungakwazi **"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "You can get water from many sources. The safest water is often from a tap. "
msgstr "Ungathola amanzi emithonjeni eminingi. Amanzi aphephe kakhulu ngokuvamile aphuma empompini. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Water from unprotected streams, open sources (such as a lake), and open dug wells are not safe. That water may have bugs (parasites) or poo from animals and or humans that can make us sick."
msgstr "Amanzi aphuma emifudlaneni engavikelekile, imithonjeni evulekile (njengechibi), nasemithonjeni embiwe evulekile awaphephile. Lawo manzi angase abe nezimbungulu (izimuncagazi) noma indle yezilwane noma abantu engasigulisa."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If you are worried about the quality of your water, boiling water can make it safe to drink and cook with:"
msgstr "Uma ukhathazeka ngokuhlanzeka kwamanzi akho, ukuwabilisa kwenza ukwazi ukuwaphuza nokupheka ngawo:"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "1ï¸âƒ£ Let the water sit for some time until the dirt settles at the bottom."
msgstr "1ï¸âƒ£ Wahlalise isikhashana ukuze udoti ukwazi ukuzika phansi."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2ï¸âƒ£ Pour it into a pot or kettle and boil it for at least 10 minutes to make sure all the germs are killed before using it."
msgstr "2ï¸âƒ£ Wafake ebhodweni noma eketeleni ukuze uwabilise okungenani imizuzu engu-10 ukuze uqinisekise ukuthi wonke amangciwane asefile ngaphambi kokuba uwasebenzise."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "3ï¸âƒ£ Drink the water within 24 hours. This helps to keep it clean, fresh, and free from other germs."
msgstr "3ï¸âƒ£ Waphuze emahoreni angu-24. Lokhu kugcina amanzi ahlale ehlanzekile, emasha, futhi engenawo amangciwane."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "2ï¸âƒ£ **Keep Water Safely in a Container**"
