#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "If you store ğŸª£ water, make sure that it does not come into contact with ğŸ–ğŸ¾ hands, dirt or ğŸ¦Ÿinsects. Hands, dirt, and insects make water unsafe to drink."
msgstr "Uma uwangcina esitsheniğŸª£ amanzi, qinisekisa ukuthi awuwathinti ğŸ–ğŸ¾ ngezandla, ukungcola noma ğŸ¦Ÿizinabhuzane azikwazi ukungena. Izandla, ukungcola, kanye nezinambuzane zenza amanzi angaphephi ukuwaphuza."

#. type=text
