msgctxt "text"
msgid "4ï¸âƒ£ **Keep Your Cooking Space Clean**"
msgstr "4ï¸âƒ£ **Gcina Indawo Ophekela Kuyo Ihlanzekile**"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Small germs that cause disease can transfer from your unwashed hands, chopping boards, cloths, and utensils.  Keep these clean."
msgstr "Amagciwane amancane abangela izifo angasuka ezandleni zakho ezingageziwe, ebhodini lokuqobela kanye nasezitsheni. Gcina lezi zinto zihlanzekile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Wash your hands with soap before touching food and while cooking."
msgstr "âœ… Geza izandla zakho ngamanzi anensipho ngaphambi kokuthinta ukudla kanye nalapho usupheka."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Wash your hands after going to the toilet."
msgstr "âœ… Geza izandla zakho ngemva kokusebenzisa idlu yangasese."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Clean your cooking space and tools every time you use them."
msgstr "âœ… Hlanza indawo ophekela kuyo kanye nezinto ozozisebenzisa njalo uma uzisebenzisa."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Keep bugs, rats, and other animals away from the cooking area."
msgstr "âœ… Izimbungulu, amagundane kanye nezinye izilwane makube kude le nendawo yokuphekela."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Cover food if you can. "
msgstr "âœ… Uma ungakwazi kumboze ukudla. "

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Remember to wash your fruits and vegetables with safe water."
msgstr "âœ… Khumbula ukugeza izithelo kanye nemifino ngamanzi ahlanzekile."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "5ï¸âƒ£ **Separate Raw and Cooked Food**"
msgstr "5ï¸âƒ£ **Hlukanisa Ukudla Okuluhlaza Kokuphekiwe**"

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "Germs causing diseases can be found in raw food (such as meat, chicken, and seafood). These can be transferred to other foods when you prepare or store food.  Separating raw and cooked food is therefore important."
msgstr "Amagciwane abangela izifo angatholakala ekudleni okungaphekiwe (njenge nyama, inkukhu, inyama eqamuka olwandle). Lamagciwane angaya kwezinye izindawo lapho usakulungiselela ukudla noma ukubeka. Kungakho kubalulekile ukuhlukanisa ukudla okuphekiwe nokungaphekiwe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Wash your knife and cutting board after cutting raw meat, chicken, or fish before using them to cut other foods."
msgstr "âœ… Geza umbese kanye nebhodi lokuqobela ngemva kokusika inyama engaphekiwe, inkukhu noma ufishi ngaphambi kokuba uqobe okunye ukudla."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Store food in covered containers when you can. This will keep it safe from insects, rats, moisture, rot, and also stop the mixing of raw and prepared foods."
msgstr "âœ… Uma ungakwazi gcina ukudla kusesitsheni esivaliwe. Lokhu kuzokuvikela ezinambuzaneni, emagundaneni, nasekuboleni futhi kuzovimba ukuxubane kokudla okuphekiwe kokungaphekiwe."

#. type=text
msgctxt "text"
msgid "âœ… Clean up any leftover ingredients when done, especially raw meat."
msgstr "âœ… Uma usuqedile coca konke okungenzeka kusalile ngenkathi upheka ikakhulukazi okokudla okungaphekiwe."

